<plot>Jesus returns to see "The Passion," and is shocked to discover that instead of focusing on his life and teachings, people are focusing on his death and suffering; things he would rather forget. Exiting the theater, he realizes that he has arrived on Earth right before the "Shabbos" resulting in a frantic search for a synagogue before sundown. His efforts are disrupted by a curmudgeonly priest, who demands that Jesus reveal his Second Coming, whether he wants to or not.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?104755</url></doc>
